                <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Every worker and task lives as a multidimensional vector on a fixed 0&ndash;10 scale, stored and indexed with pgvector in PostgreSQL.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-6 transition-colors hover:border-brand/40 dark:border-gray-700 dark:bg-gray-900">
