                <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Every recommendation is backed by transparent math you can audit &mdash; a reliable answer to why each person was ranked where they are.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-6 transition-colors hover:border-brand/40 dark:border-gray-700 dark:bg-gray-900">
