    <!-- How it works -->
    <section id="how-it-works" class="bg-gray-100 py-20 dark:bg-gray-900/50">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 sm:px-6">
            <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center">
                <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-brand">How it works</p>
                <h2 class="mt-3 text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-balance text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl dark:text-gray-100">From skills to assignment in four steps</h2>
            </div>
            <ol class="mt-14 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
                <li class="relative rounded-xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-6 dark:border-gray-700 dark:bg-gray-900">
                    <span class="font-mono text-3xl font-bold text-brand/25">01</span>
                    <h3 class="mt-3 text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Model your team</h3>
                    <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Score each developer's skills from 0 to 10. Every profile becomes a vector stored in an indexed pgvector column.</p>
                </li>
                <li class="relative rounded-xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-6 dark:border-gray-700 dark:bg-gray-900">
                    <span class="font-mono text-3xl font-bold text-brand/25">02</span>
                    <h3 class="mt-3 text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Define the task</h3>
                    <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Set the minimum required skill levels for a task. That requirement is just another vector in the same space.</p>
                </li>
                <li class="relative rounded-xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-6 dark:border-gray-700 dark:bg-gray-900">
                    <span class="font-mono text-3xl font-bold text-brand/25">03</span>
                    <h3 class="mt-3 text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Match by similarity</h3>
                    <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Cosine similarity ranks candidates instantly, surfacing best-fit, growth, and fastest-to-finish options.</p>
                </li>
                <li class="relative rounded-xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-6 dark:border-gray-700 dark:bg-gray-900">
                    <span class="font-mono text-3xl font-bold text-brand/25">04</span>
                    <h3 class="mt-3 text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Evaluate &amp; recalculate</h3>
                    <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">When work ships, performance and deliverable criticality feed back into each profile, sharpening future matches.</p>
                </li>
            </ol>
